Package: gac
Version: 0.0.9000
Date: 2020-04-28
Title: Genetic Analysis of Cells
Authors@R: person("Rodrigo Gularte Merida", "Developer", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "gularter@mskcc.org")
Author: Rodrigo Gularte Merida [aut, cre]
